WEBVTT

00:04:59.679 --> 00:05:03.211
This would transform
an unpopular carbon tax

00:05:03.235 --> 00:05:06.477
into a popular and populist solution,

00:05:06.501 --> 00:05:08.325
and it would also solve

00:05:08.349 --> 00:05:11.662
the underlying psychological barrier
that we discussed,

00:05:11.686 --> 00:05:16.363
by giving everyone a concrete benefit
in the here and now.

00:05:17.307 --> 00:05:19.596
And these benefits would be significant.

00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:23.362
Assuming a carbon tax rate
that starts at 40 dollars per ton,

00:05:23.386 --> 00:05:26.809
a family of four would receive
2,000 dollars per year

00:05:26.833 --> 00:05:28.064
from the get-go.

00:05:28.643 --> 00:05:30.886
According to the US Treasury Department,